<span id="freeTextContainer8018807643743511930">When pastry chef Jane Gray tries to sell her daughter&apos;s locket, she becomes the unlikely subject of a massive police hunt and fodder for London&apos;s tabloid press. Secrets unravel, lies are exposed, and the Duke of Rutledge demands custody of his niece. <br/><br/>Charming and handsome, the duke&apos;s brother Finn spends his leisure time between the sheets of London&apos;s most beautiful, wanton</span>
  <span id="freeText8018807643743511930" style="display:none">When pastry chef Jane Gray tries to sell her daughter's locket, she becomes the unlikely subject of a massive police hunt and fodder for London's tabloid press. Secrets unravel, lies are exposed, and the Duke of Rutledge demands custody of his niece. <br /><br />Charming and handsome, the duke's brother Finn spends his leisure time between the sheets of London's most beautiful, wanton women. The seasoned rake is perplexed by his attraction to demure, virtuous Jane... definitely not his usual type. Finn soon learns there is more to Jane than meets the eye and he longs to possess the passionate woman hidden beneath her modest facade.<br /><br />When publicity draws the attention of a madman from Jane's past, Finn enters London's dangerous underworld in a heart-stopping race to save her.</span>
