    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_444664441" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/444664441" />
    <a title="Sandy Loyd" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11567598-sandy-loyd"><img alt="Sandy Loyd" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442637647p2/11567598.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/444664441?book_show_action=true">Oct 30, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sandy Loyd" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sandy Loyd" href="/user/show/11567598-sandy-loyd">Sandy Loyd</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer444664441" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13448528064614534190">I really enjoyed The Promise by Kate Worth. Her characters were fun and likable (lovable actually) and her details about the time were excellent. I felt like I had stepped back into time and was sorry to come to the end. I&apos;m now wondering if Ms. Worth will write a sequel. There are several characters I&apos;d love to know more about.</span>
  <span id="freeText13448528064614534190" style="display:none">I really enjoyed The Promise by Kate Worth. Her characters were fun and likable (lovable actually) and her details about the time were excellent. I felt like I had stepped back into time and was sorry to come to the end. I'm now wondering if Ms. Worth will write a sequel. There are several characters I'd love to know more about.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13448528064614534190" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


