<span id="freeTextContainer39052637203931702">I loved this book! it&apos;s my first romance and it was well worth stepping out of my usual reading style. This book for me was a mixture of hot, warm and cold. The sex was hot the characters were warm and life like, and the evil cousin Tom was cold as ice. The real affection this family had for each other was one of the things that made me believe these were real people not just characters in a book, they came to life for me. The attention to detail is really what makes this such a good read, the b</span>
  <span id="freeText39052637203931702" style="display:none">I loved this book! it's my first romance and it was well worth stepping out of my usual reading style. This book for me was a mixture of hot, warm and cold. The sex was hot the characters were warm and life like, and the evil cousin Tom was cold as ice. The real affection this family had for each other was one of the things that made me believe these were real people not just characters in a book, they came to life for me. The attention to detail is really what makes this such a good read, the book made me feel like I had stepped back in time just for a while. I can't even imagine the research that was involved to get this so spot on. I can't wait for her next book, who's romantic life will we get to watch unfold next time. </span>
